"Stand up now!"
"Look straight ahead!"
"Show them", he whispered to them, "how pretty girls are!"
Four girls, barely teenagers, with white gloves and identical olive-green jackets and trousers stood up tight.
Four pairs of black pumps were in a straight line.
Four neat hats sat perfectly on the hair held in blue and white striped loops.
"To me they look average", Mr. Tang says contemptuously.
"Models are pretty".
