He wanted to know if the baby was his, but his ex-wife never let him run a DNA test.
Soon after, she entered into another relationship.
The one chosen was Alberto, a young man from Lousame, a neighboring community.
She lived with him for a long time.
César lived with them.
When the young woman went to the Balearic Islands to look for work, the little one stayed with her partner, who even accompanied her to Palma for a week.
But from the content of their messages, it can be concluded that their love affair broke down and they separated.
In March 2008, she is alone in Menorca and writes: "Alberto is very strange and angry because I came here to work".
