"On the one hand, César is satisfied, on the other, not".
"On the one hand, he's with me and he likes the place a little bit, but on the other hand, he has to go to school every day".
She's talking about moving to Mallorca.
"He's going to summer school there, so I'll have less expenses for the nanny".
On the 17th, memories and lamentations.
"A big kiss from César, asking me when you'll be back".
"Alberto says he's e-mailed me some videos, you know, if he wants to find me, he can, that's bullshit".
On the 30th, another: "The boy is doing well, he's going to summer school to learn Catalan".
One of them, from her current partner, Víctor, says: "He's throwing money at me".
On the Internet, in anime and manga blogs, there are messages from her.
